Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.04,0:44:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ben.\N- Rõ!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.11,0:44:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Cameron.\N- Rõ!
